    summary: 'Sebelum dunia memiliki bentuk, Atum-Ra muncul sendirian dari lautan purba Nun di atas gundukan tanah pertama, lalu air mata yang tumpah dari Matanya yang murka melahirkan umat manusia pertama.',
    summaryEn: 'Before the world had form, Atum-Ra rose alone from the primordial waters of Nun upon the first mound of earth, and the tears that fell from his furious Eye gave birth to the first human beings.',
